74
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:19,350
<i>Veď smrť je taká bolestivá.</i>

75
00:06:19,350 --> 00:06:21,460
<i>Máš len jednu možnosť.</i>

76
00:06:21,460 --> 00:06:23,020
<i>Nie.</i>

77
00:06:24,590 --> 00:06:26,370
